    <summary>Windows-native CLI for window management, input automation, UI inspection, screenshots, and wait primitives.</summary>
    <description>peekwin is a Windows-native CLI for OS-level automation. It exposes focused primitives for window management, input simulation, UI inspection, screenshots, clipboard access, and wait-based synchronization.</description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/usamaejaz/peekwin/releases/tag/v__VERSION__</releaseNotes>
    <tags>windows automation cli win32 ui-automation screenshot input clipboard wait</tags>
